              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3">
                <span class="text-gray-300">Registration and Submission of Fee</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-medium">Jun 22-29</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3">
                <span class="text-gray-300">Youm e Ashura**</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-medium">Jun 25</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-600/10 rounded-lg p-3 border border-cyan-500/30">
                <span class="text-white font-semibold">Commencement of Classes for Summer Semester</span>
