              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3">
                <span class="text-gray-300">Comprehensive Examination of PhD</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-medium">Jul 01-03</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3">
                <span class="text-gray-300">Submission of Six Monthly report by PhD & MS/MPhil/MSc(Hons) scholars</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-medium">Jul 17</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-orange-600/10 rounded-lg p-3 border border-orange-500/30">
