              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500/20 to-red-600/10 rounded-lg p-3 border border-red-500/30">
                <span class="text-white font-semibold">Final Term Examination***</span>
